  <brief_title>MRI Guided High Intensity Focused Ultrasound (HIFU) and ThermoDox for Palliation of Painful Bone Metastases</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Trial of Phillips MRI-Guided High Intensity Focused Ultrasound (Sonalleve) and Lyso-thermosensitive Liposomal Doxorubicin (ThermoDox) for Palliation of Painful Bone Metastases</official_title>
