  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate treatment with High Intensity Focused Ultrasound (HIFU)in
      combination with ThermoDox (liposomal doxorubicin) is safe and effective in reducing pain for
      patients with painful bone metastases.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
